OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FKey consumer protection    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpowers come into force     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, New rules for consumer protection      
OL,6, across financial services to ensure    
OL,7, people are treated fairly have come    
OL,8, into force.                            
OL,10,FThe new Consumer Duty is supposed to   
OL,11,Fensure people are served by financial  
OL,12,Fproducts they can understand.          
OL,14,FIt aims to end hidden charges, and     
OL,15,Fensure providers of products such as   
OL,16,Fsavings accounts and mortgages inform  
OL,17,Fpeople of any better deals available.  
OL,19,FBut commentators say some businesses   
OL,20,Fare ill-prepared for the changes.      
